On the day before, i.e. on December 20, three concerts will take place at the same time as 21:00 in Prague, Brno and Ostrava.
The end of the concert should be at about the time the Maya calendar ends on the Pacific island of Kiribati, located in a time zone 12 hours before us.
Who's the source of this idea?
Originally probably from me, then we designed the idea together with our graphic artist Honza Augusta.
